data.title: AWS Builder Profile
data.description:
Contributed to the AWS Builder Profile, a marketing tool for AWS to store and maintain customer data of AWS users -
 - Led development of LLM based moderation of profile fields and community honor badges 
 - Used Typescript, React, and AWS

data.title: AWS Pulse
data.description:
Contributed to AWS Pulse, Amazon's company-wide internal survey and feedback tool 
 - Led development of site-site accessibility improvements 
 - Used Typescript, React, and AWS

data.title: Bifrost
data.description:
Developed an approximate quantum transpiler for variational quantum algorithms 
 - Presented initial findings at APS March Meeting 2024 
 - Submitted technical paper to IEEE QCE 2025 
 - Used Python, Qiskit, and TorchQuantum

data.title: IVM
data.description:
Worked on IVM, a dataset for tracking relationships between government initiatives in the Department of Veterans Affairs 
 - Developed a recommender system to provide users suggested related initiatives when they are adding new initiatives to the IVM dataset 
 - Used Python and PyTorch
